pageContext.claim: “Getting ready to leave for one of my favorite places, the Florida Panhandle, where we've given, and are giving, billions of $$$ for the devastation caused by Hurricane Michael. Even though the Dems are totally in our way (they don't want money to go there) we're getting it done!”
pageContext.analysis: Democrats did not try to block aid to Florida. The hitch in securing the funding was Trump's refusal to give money to Puerto Rico.
